➜潮到爆表！吉利星瑞华南首秀，抖in星潮生活节了解一下
http://www.sohu.com/a/426811104_99994080	35223
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201023/f25a7609493043e0af8134290921b776.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201023/6240e5e270bd4965a498e3eed3a006b9.png" max-width="600" /></p>
